          Press '?' key for on-line help
Burt is awake again.  You may address messages to 'gm'
(no quotes) to log messages to labc-4lc (Van A. Boughner)
in a file and hear a response from Burt code.  Thanks.

*** New: place cursor on objects and press i to see info.

